		<item>
			<title>Version 0.1.3</title>
			<description>
				<![CDATA[
					<h2>Version 0.1.3 - Complete Feature Release</h2>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>AppleScript Support</strong> - Execute custom AppleScript for UI automation and system control</li>
						<li><strong>Swift Expressions</strong> - Evaluate Swift expressions for calculations and simple operations</li>
						<li><strong>Permission Management</strong> - Comprehensive dialogs with step-by-step guidance</li>
						<li><strong>Window Foreground Fix</strong> - App now always opens in front of other windows</li>
						<li><strong>Error Handling</strong> - Improved messages with actionable solutions</li>
						<li><strong>Release Automation</strong> - Enhanced build and deployment tools</li>
					</ul>
				]]>
			</description>
